## 2026-04-03 - Template flow and full dialog are disconnected creation paths
- Removed `ApplyForm` component (~450 lines) and replaced the `if (selectedTemplate)` render branch in `GraphPanel` with `TokenGeneratorDialog` pre-filled via the `template` prop. When a template is selected, the full dialog now opens with: generator type pre-selected, target group pre-filled from `template.defaultPrefix`, config pre-loaded from `template.config`, source token pre-filled from `pendingGroupPath` (when triggered from token badge), and type hint from `pendingGroupTokenType`. Template's `semanticLayers` are applied automatically in `onSaved` via a best-effort POST/PATCH loop, with `onInterceptSemanticMapping={() => {}}` suppressing the dialog's own suggestion. Removed `allTokensFlat` from `GraphPanelProps` and App.tsx call site since `TokenGeneratorDialog` handles its own source-token autocomplete. Removed unused imports: `getErrorMessage`, `Spinner`, `AliasAutocomplete`, `isDimensionLike`, `GeneratedTokenResult`, `useCallback`, `TokenMapEntry`.
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/GraphPanel.tsx` ~L1-10 (imports), ~L471-922 (ApplyForm removed), ~L1003-1016 (selectedTemplate block), `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/App.tsx` ~L2341 (allTokensFlat prop removed)
- **Learnings for future iterations:**

